The paper deals with object detection, which is a core problem in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves optimizing the region selection strategy, which is a machine learning task (cs.LG). The authors use a CNN-based framework, which is a popular approach in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The evaluation is performed on image datasets, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) categories.
